long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Handless Millionaire is a fun but bloody reaction game in which you will leave the field either as a millionaire or as a penniless loser without arms. Have you always dreamed of testing your knowledge on the famous TV show "Who Wants to be a Millionaire"? Then you've come to the right place! However, you won't be facing a moderator who will ask you questions, but a merciless guillotine.

Note: Also added many different games.

You can play all Categories Game in This Extension.

Controls: Mouse
